==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Antipope
<hw>An"ti*pope</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is
elected, or claims to be, pope in opposition to the pope canonically
chosen; esp. applied to those popes who resided at Avignon during the
Great Schism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Antipsoric</ent>⟦br⟧
